"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/27>`_)."
msgstr ""
"如果你遇到的是 ``Python int too large to convert to C long`` 这个特定错误，可以参考 "
"`PyTorch 修复方案 "
"<https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/issues/162430#issuecomment-3289054096>`_，其中涉及对"
" ``torch_python.dll`` 打补丁（参见 `#27 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/27>`_）。"

#: ../../faq.rst:49 604b06682bb54985a9068cd50ebc5b6e
msgid "torchcodec / libtorchcodec errors"
msgstr "torchcodec / libtorchcodec 报错"

#: ../../faq.rst:51 20873fc3964a4affb973310ec6e7c98b
msgid ""
"**Symptom:** ``RuntimeError: Could not load libtorchcodec`` or "
"``ImportError: TorchCodec is required for load_with_torchcodec`` when "
"using voice cloning with a reference audio."
msgstr ""
"**现象：** 在使用参考音频进行声音克隆时，出现 ``RuntimeError: Could not load libtorchcodec`` "
"或 ``ImportError: TorchCodec is required for load_with_torchcodec``。"

#: ../../faq.rst:53 eb3590f98bb545ba9a9308190c1af91b
msgid ""
"**Cause:** ``torchaudio`` (>= 2.9) uses ``torchcodec`` as its default "
"audio backend, which requires FFmpeg to be properly installed."
msgstr ""
"**原因：** ``torchaudio``（>= 2.9）默认使用 ``torchcodec`` 作为音频后端，而它要求系统正确安装 "
"FFmpeg。"

#: ../../faq.rst:57 91488f3fa88e4b1bb87138970abae939
msgid "Install FFmpeg system-wide (version 4–7 supported):"
msgstr "在系统范围安装 FFmpeg（支持 4–7 版本）："

#: ../../faq.rst:59 ab6d08af7cf64bb5bcdfec1c1fd28f08
msgid "**Linux:** ``sudo apt install ffmpeg``"
msgstr "**Linux：** ``sudo apt install ffmpeg``"

#: ../../faq.rst:60 fe053678ef674ad4b72ec6a4cbefe820
msgid "**macOS:** ``brew install ffmpeg``"
msgstr "**macOS：** ``brew install ffmpeg``"

#: ../../faq.rst:61 a5111ae42ba844b4aa287222296c69ab
msgid ""
"**Windows:** Download from `ffmpeg.org "
"<https://ffmpeg.org/download.html>`_ and add to ``PATH``"
msgstr ""
"**Windows：** 从 `ffmpeg.org <https://ffmpeg.org/download.html>`_ 下载，并加入 "
"``PATH``"

#: ../../faq.rst:63 b7a0989bfef44f2a8083ad56efdc8cf0
msgid "Install a compatible torchcodec version:"
msgstr "安装兼容的 torchcodec 版本："

