#: ../../faq.rst:80 8f859695a16d45cb8ff3d7bdc1b1212a
msgid "torch.compile errors on first run"
msgstr "首次运行时的 torch.compile 报错"

#: ../../faq.rst:82 a74f11a636384d66a368d88e97e9487e
msgid ""
"**Symptom:** ``torch._dynamo.exc.Unsupported`` errors (often mentioning "
"``einops`` or ``symmetric_difference``) during the warm-up phase."
msgstr ""
"**现象：** 在预热阶段出现 ``torch._dynamo.exc.Unsupported`` 错误（通常会提到 ``einops`` 或 "
"``symmetric_difference``）。"

#: ../../faq.rst:84 4a2ff4f1dd1c42b0bfd9ffdc52740f1e
msgid ""
"**Cause:** Certain combinations of PyTorch, Triton, and einops versions "
"have incompatibilities with ``torch.compile`` (`#19 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/19>`_)."
msgstr ""
"**原因：** 某些 PyTorch、Triton 与 einops 的版本组合与 ``torch.compile`` 不兼容（参见 `#19 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/19>`_）。"

