#: ../../faq.rst:115 922534a4d4884f1b9efa9d3ae62226b0
msgid "Mac / MPS support"
msgstr "Mac / MPS 支持"

#: ../../faq.rst:117 f10dd2142357463abb94b57dea201b5e
msgid "**Q: Can VoxCPM run on Mac (Apple Silicon)?**"
msgstr "**问：VoxCPM 可以在 Mac（Apple Silicon）上运行吗？**"

#: ../../faq.rst:119 94a2fc7254be4aa7a6e25c52162d69e5
msgid ""
"Yes. VoxCPM supports CPU and MPS (Metal Performance Shaders) on Apple "
"Silicon Macs (`#14 <https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/14>`_, `#20 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/20>`_, `#41 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/41>`_)."
msgstr ""
"可以。VoxCPM 支持在 Apple Silicon Mac 上使用 CPU 和 MPS（Metal Performance "
"Shaders）（参见 `#14 <https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/14>`_、`#20 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/20>`_、`#41 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/41>`_）。"

#: ../../faq.rst:121 8235904dad764c0095eed16d8f0439d9
msgid ""
"**CPU:** Works out of the box, but inference is slow (`#67 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/67>`_)."
msgstr ""
"**CPU：** 开箱即用，但推理速度较慢（参见 `#67 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/67>`_）。"

#: ../../faq.rst:122 c47d7b2ae81e46a8935e122fa565c74d
msgid ""
"**MPS:** ``device=\"auto\"`` will try MPS automatically when CUDA is "
"unavailable."
msgstr "**MPS：** 当 CUDA 不可用时，``device=\"auto\"`` 会自动尝试使用 MPS。"

#: ../../faq.rst:126 298aba3e22fe49bf87378d793f8c8f29
msgid ""
"The denoiser (ZipEnhancer) runs on CPU even when MPS is active. If you "
"don't need prompt speech enhancement, set ``load_denoiser=False`` to save"
" memory."
msgstr ""
"即使启用了 MPS，降噪器（ZipEnhancer）仍然运行在 CPU 上。如果你不需要增强 prompt 语音，可设置 "
"``load_denoiser=False`` 以节省内存。"

#: ../../faq.rst:130 df854ca7d18b4f67b1daddb052a27a9a
msgid ""
"``torch.backends.mps.is_available()`` only means the MPS backend exists. "
"It does not guarantee that every VoxCPM inference path will run "
"successfully on that backend. If you hit a runtime error on MPS, "
"explicitly switch to CPU:"
msgstr ""
"``torch.backends.mps.is_available()`` 只表示 MPS 后端存在。它并不保证 VoxCPM 的所有推理路径都能在该后端上成功运行。"
"如果你在 MPS 上遇到运行时错误，请显式切换到 CPU："

#: ../../faq.rst:144 049cbf9de3284cbaa303b4860f6ff09b
msgid "WSL2 / ROCm community workaround"
msgstr "WSL2 / ROCm 社区 workaround"

#: ../../faq.rst:146 84c04d0464f0413aa56e29d843f7d8a0
msgid "**Q: Can VoxCPM run on AMD ROCm under WSL2?**"
msgstr "**问：VoxCPM 可以在 WSL2 下的 AMD ROCm 环境中运行吗？**"

#: ../../faq.rst:148 9ba5885f96324c86918a8bb050903330
msgid ""
"There is a community-reported path for WSL2 + ROCm, but it is not one of "
"the project's primary tested environments. In the report from `#203 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/203>`_, the user needed two "
"workarounds:"
msgstr ""
"社区中已有在 WSL2 + ROCm 上运行的案例，但这并不是项目当前的主要测试环境之一。"
"在 `#203 <https://github.com/OpenBMB/VoxCPM/issues/203>`_ 的报告中，用户需要两个 workaround："

#: ../../faq.rst:152 6ab7a604be0a4c8d8a9b7d8ee16d17f5
msgid ""
"Monkey-patch ``torchaudio.load_with_torchcodec`` / "
"``save_with_torchcodec`` back to the standard ``torchaudio`` I/O "
"functions because ``torchcodec`` was not working in that ROCm setup."
msgstr ""
"将 ``torchaudio.load_with_torchcodec`` / ``save_with_torchcodec`` monkey-patch "
"回标准的 ``torchaudio`` I/O 函数，因为该 ROCm 环境中的 ``torchcodec`` 无法正常工作。"

#: ../../faq.rst:155 0469b82832394515b877b2689c6b46b3
msgid "Disable ``torch.compile`` by setting ``optimize=False``."
msgstr "通过设置 ``optimize=False`` 禁用 ``torch.compile``。"

#: ../../faq.rst:157 97a1e01e87b64d2ba6b853a313ed1988
msgid ""
"If you are experimenting with ROCm or other non-CUDA platforms, start by "
"disabling ``torch.compile`` first:"
msgstr "如果你正在尝试 ROCm 或其他非 CUDA 平台，建议先从禁用 ``torch.compile`` 开始："

#: ../../faq.rst:164 dacf08ce3f484d848493e8beb01a0920
msgid ""
"If your environment still fails on the default device path, explicitly "
"fall back to CPU and validate the rest of the pipeline before trying any "
"additional acceleration settings."
msgstr "如果你的环境在默认设备路径下仍然失败，请先显式回退到 CPU，验证其余流程可用后，再尝试额外的加速设置。"

