msgstr "Python 版本兼容性"

#: ../../faq.rst:171 e1623a7427a64214a305ec1b68d91634
msgid ""
"VoxCPM is most tested on **Python 3.10–3.11**. For current releases, "
"**Python 3.10–3.12** is the recommended runtime range. Known issues:"
